{"tid":449668,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"【Ig新功能】直播時邀請觀眾一齊Live","createTime":"2017-10-27T11:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T11:28:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed59f8b0a9c9fab7bc05ede8f09b217f4ccc8ae2","tid":449668,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20171027/20195593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195593&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=4032c929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195593&h=53ad30db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20171027/20195593</a><br />\n<br />\n【Ig新功能】直播時邀請觀眾一齊Live<br />\n<br />\nTechnology   <br />\n         <br />\n全新旅遊專頁，即like籽想旅行：<a href=\"https://fb.com/travel.appleseed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Ftravel.appleseed&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bfb9b31a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/travel.appleseed</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20171027/large/sub5301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20171027%2Flarge%2Fsub5301.jpg&h=a1f136b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nInstagram新加入「Go Live With」功能。<br />\n<br />\n唔少朋友都會在Instagram上開直播，不過一人Live似乎有點悶，最新版本Instagram就加入新「Go Live With」功能，等用家在直播時隨時邀請觀眾一齊Live！這個新功能在8月時已開始測試，不過當時只限少數用家有得試，現時就開放給所有Ig用家。當然直播控制權是落在原本用家手上，除了可以邀請觀眾加入外，如果對方唔啱傾或太搶風頭，亦可以隨時將佢踢走！觀眾當然在收到直播邀請時，亦有權唔玩。直播完成後，亦可以好似之前Ig直播一樣，可將直播影片儲存在Stories發佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20171027/large/sub5302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20171027%2Flarge%2Fsub5302.jpg&h=2f7e3157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當邀請了觀眾一同直播時，手機畫面會以上下分割畫面顯示。<br />\n<br />\n記者：布偉倫"}]}